commitResults.messageTitle: Renamed to Meow.java, added new logo and greeting. Level-0 completed.
Add new feature of echoing the users input. Infinite user loop until user inputs 'bye'. Level 1 completed.
Add functional list. Supported ability for user to add tasks via String input. And To show tasks via the list command. Level-2 Completed.
Add Task class to help manage tasks and data.
Add support for functional mark / unmark list. Added some error handling, to validate inputs. Level 3 done.

Add Deadline, Event, Todo classes to enforce speical and unique types of tasks. Added error handling, and input validation to ensure Deadlines, event and todo tasks are properly formatted and inputted. Thus, no blanks, or missing fields.
